title: Premium SEO Pack v1.9.0 - Premium WordPress Plugins
description:
The Premium SEO Pack for WordPress is the ultimate tool for optimizing your website for today's search engines. Premium SEO Pack contains all the features that you would expect to find in dozens of different WordPress plugins, plus it includes unique features that you just cannot find anywhere else. Contains external links.

To install:
1. Upload the folder to the /wp-content/plugins/ directory
2. Activate the plugin through the 'Plugins' menu in WordPress
